cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.SI

This paper deals with the problem of learning GANs from non-iid data in a decentralized manner, which involves techniques from machine learning (cs.LG), distributed computing (cs.DC), computer vision (cs.CV), and security and privacy (cs.CR, cs.SI). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG, followed by cs.DC and cs.CV. The paper also discusses privacy concerns, which could fall under cs.CR and cs.SI.
